Suppose that a group of patients with a certain disease are being treated with a new drug. The survival time for each patient is recorded in days starting from the beginning of their treatment. The following are the survival times (in days) for a sample of 10 patients:

{120, 45, 60, 90, 10, 200, 180, 50, 30, 75}

Calculate the median survival time of patients using the Kaplan-Meier estimator method.
